	<body>
		<media type="m:text" id="2001" mode="8" name="Tips" filename="1146767254752.xml" />
		<paragraph type="text" x="12" y="+16" width="407" height="0" style="normal" tabs="" indent="0">&lt;TEXTFORMAT LEADING=&quot;2&quot;&gt;&lt;P ALIGN=&quot;LEFT&quot;&gt;&lt;FONT FACE=&quot;Verdana&quot; SIZE=&quot;13&quot; COLOR=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;Chart A shows a general downward trend [1] the decade in the number of hours per week spent watching television. From just under 23.5 hours [2] 1991, the number of viewing hours fell steadily [3] 1995, when there was a marked rise. [4] 1996 and 1998 there was another steady decline. [5] 1999 there was a sharp drop of nearly an hour. Time spent viewing continued to decline steadily [6] the rest of the period.&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;/TEXTFORMAT&gt;</paragraph>
		<paragraph type="text" x="12" y="+0" width="407" height="0" style="normal" tabs="" indent="0">&lt;TEXTFORMAT LEADING=&quot;2&quot;&gt;&lt;P ALIGN=&quot;LEFT&quot;&gt;&lt;FONT FACE=&quot;_sans&quot; SIZE=&quot;12&quot; COLOR=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt; &lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;/TEXTFORMAT&gt;</paragraph>
		<paragraph type="text" x="12" y="+0" width="407" height="0" style="normal" tabs="" indent="0">&lt;TEXTFORMAT LEADING=&quot;2&quot;&gt;&lt;P ALIGN=&quot;LEFT&quot;&gt;&lt;FONT FACE=&quot;Verdana&quot; SIZE=&quot;13&quot; COLOR=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;Line graph B shows variations in audience size for Channel 1 [7] different times [8] an average weekday. The first peak in audience figures comes [9] 1 o&apos;clock in the afternoon, when around 35 per cent of the population are watching. However, it is clear that prime time for Channel 1 is [10] the early evening. [11] 6 p.m. well over 50 per cent of the population are tuned in and [12] 7 p.m. [13] 10 p.m. at least two-fifths of the population are watching. Not surprisingly, the percentage falls off dramatically [14] midnight. [15] 3 a.m. only a tiny proportion of the population are watching and figure does not rise significantly [16] 10 a.m. in the morning.&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;/TEXTFORMAT&gt;</paragraph>
		<paragraph type="text" x="12" y="+0" width="407" height="0" style="normal" tabs="" indent="0">&lt;TEXTFORMAT LEADING=&quot;2&quot;&gt;&lt;P ALIGN=&quot;LEFT&quot;&gt;&lt;FONT FACE=&quot;_sans&quot; SIZE=&quot;12&quot; COLOR=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt; &lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;/TEXTFORMAT&gt;</paragraph>
